Payment Options 
Manage My Account
With your online account, you can: 

Make a one-time payment with your savings or checking account at no charge
Set up recurring/direct debit payments
View Budget Billing Details
Opt in for Paperless Billing
View your current and past South Jersey Gas Bills
Much more! Create or log in to your account for details

Don't have an account? You can create your account at the link below.
Create An Account or Log in to Manage My Account

One-Time Payment with EZ-Pay
Make a quick one-time payment with a checking account, savings account, credit card or debit card without an online account. A $1.99 fee applies. 

Pay Now

Automated Payments
Want to save time and money with automated payments from your checking or savings account? There are two ways to register for automated payments: Online or via U.S. mail. 


Enroll in Recurring Payments

Log in to Manage My Account and enroll in Recurring Payments. It's quick and easy and you can set dollar limits on how much can be paid via Recurring Payments. 
Log in to Manage My Account

Enroll in Direct Debit via U.S. Mail

Fill out, sign and mail to:
South Jersey Gas
PO Box 6091
Bellmawr, NJ 08099-6091
Download Form (PDF)
 


Budget Billing/Equal Payment Plan
Want to know exactly how much you'll pay each month? Enroll in our budget billing program. 
Keep in mind: 

We review your monthly payment amounts one or more times each year to ensure your payment is based on how much natural gas you use
If you don't pay your budget billing payments on time, we may have to remove you from the Budget Billing program

Enroll in Budget Billing
 

Paperless Billing
Want a free, fast and safe way to receive and pay your bill online? You can enroll in our Paperless Billing program with your online account.  
Paperless Billing is open to all residential and some commercial customers, but some restrictions may apply.
Log In

Pay By Mail/Pay By Phone
Mail payments to: 
South Jersey Gas
PO Box 6091 
Bellmawr, NJ 08099-6091
Want to pay by phone? If you have your South Jersey Gas account number, you can use our automated phone system to pay via Visa, MasterCard, Discover or American Express credit/debit cards or check by phone 24 hours a day at 1-866-466-1411 
A $1.99 fee applies for all payments by phone. 
 

Payment Centers
Want to pay your South Jersey Gas Bill in person? Check the interactive map below to find a payment center near you. 
 


nbsp;



Having Trouble Paying Your Bill? 
Can't pay your bill right now?  Call us at 888-766-9900 
After reviewing your account and other criteria, we'll do our best to work out a mutually agreeable payment schedule.
If your service is shut off for nonpayment, call our offices immediately at 888-766-9900 
Our Customer Care hours are 7 a.m. to 8 p.m. Monday through Friday and 9 a.m. to 2 p.m. on Saturday.
If you have trouble paying your bill regularly, you may qualify for one of several Financial Assistance Programs.
 
Financial Assistance Programs

Customers With Special Needs
Shutoff Notification Options
Senior Citizen Notification
Are you a Senior Citizen? South Jersey Gas can call you before shutting off your service for a past due bill. 
To opt in, click below or call us at 888-766-9900
Third Party Notification
Do you forget to pay sometimes or have trouble understanding when to pay your bill? South Jersey Gas can arrange to send a copy of any customer's bill to a third party when the bill includes a shutoff notice. 
To opt in, click below or call us at 888-766-9900
Landlord Notification
Are you a landlord? South Jersey Gas has a free program that helps landlords or their authorized management agents monitor the natural gas service status at their properties. 
To opt in, complete contact Customer Care at the link below or call us at 888-766-9900
Landlord Notification form
Contact Customer Care












