Overview South Jersey Gas Company is a gas transmission and distribution company in Hammonton. This private company was founded in 1910. The organization has 18 other locations.Revenue The organization generates $534M in estimated sales.Employees South Jersey Gas Company employs 475 people of which 96 employees are estimated to work at this location. In Hammonton, an average company has between 2 and 33 employees, meaning that slightly more people work at South Jersey Gas Company than at the average company.
 





