            South Jersey Gas, a part of South Jersey Industries, is a natural gas production and distribution company that serves clients in New Jersey. Founded in 1910, the company serves more than 300,000 customers. South Jersey Industries provides energy-related services and products through its various business units. The parent company also owns other unregulated businesses, including Marina Energy, South Jersey Energy, South Jersey Resources Group and South Jersey Energy Service Plus. South Jersey Energy, its subsidiary, acquires and markets natural gas and electricity for retail customers and also provides businesses with energy services to reduce their energy costs.
          






















